{"lang": "zh_CN", "eventid": "act50side", "eventName": "泡影苍霆", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "TD-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕间", "storyName": "幻梦终醒，猎魂不息", "storyInfo": "梓兰等人回到了泰拉，还带了些土特产，泡影国也回归平静，而“雷之主”，也回到了属于它的国度。风沙停歇，旭日东升。", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert03_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_sand02", "flip": 2.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "风，是这场混乱中唯一的主宰。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斑点正用他那面巨大的盾牌，艰难地为自己和身后的泡普卡撑起一片小小的、摇摇欲坠的安全区。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_284_spot_1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳......麻烦死了！这沙子都要钻进我肺里了！月见夜，你那边怎么样了？！", "name": "斑点"}, "figure_art": "char_284_spot_1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_283_midn_1#4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还行！最后两个沙盗已经被我解决了！你那边呢？泡普卡还好吗？", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "char_283_midn_1#4"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_284_spot_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她好得很，一直躲在我后面，一粒沙子都吃不着！倒是你，解决完了就快点过来帮忙！我快顶不住了！", "name": "斑点"}, "figure_art": "char_284_spot_1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的新漫画还在罗德岛等我，我可不想不明不白地死在这里！", "name": "斑点"}, "figure_art": "char_284_spot_1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_283_midn_1#4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冷静点，斑点，再坚持一下，梓兰小姐和空爆一定会来支援的！", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "char_283_midn_1#4"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（好可怕......风沙好大......我什么都看不清了......）", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#5$2"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（斑点哥哥......他的盾牌在晃......他快要顶不住了......）", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#5$2"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（咦？那个人......是沙盗！他躲过了月见夜哥哥！）", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#1$2"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斑点哥哥！", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#7$2"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_283_midn_1#4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斑点，小心身后！", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "char_283_midn_1#4"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_284_spot_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什么？！", "name": "斑点"}, "figure_art": "char_284_spot_1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（他转不过来！来不及了！那把刀......那把刀要砍下去了！）", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#5$2"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不要——不要伤害斑点哥哥！）", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#5$2"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_white", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一股奇特的、灼热的东西突然从她的眼底涌出。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她甚至来不及思考那是什么，只是遵循着本能，将那股力量对准了那个沙盗的方向。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一道几乎看不见的能量光束，从她的眼中一闪而过。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它没有击中任何人。"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 60.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_beamamb", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗡——"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一声仿佛来自大地之外的奇异嗡鸣响起，紧接着，一道无形的冲击波扩散开来。"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert03_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_283_midn_1#4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刚才那是什么？！", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "char_283_midn_1#4"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_284_spot_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道！好像有什么东西炸了？喂！泡普卡，你没事吧？！", "name": "斑点"}, "figure_art": "char_284_spot_1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......泡普卡没事......", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#4$2"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "泡普卡呆呆地站在原地，她自己也不知道刚才发生了什么。她只看到那个坏人飞了出去，斑点哥哥安全了。"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert03_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......结束了？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们......回来了？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#6$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像是......刚才那场狩猎......那个“御轮”......宝巫迦......时间过去了多久？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#6$2"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一声清脆的、与这片沙漠格格不入的叫声，从她们身后响起。"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这里......难道是远方的封印之地喵？", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$2"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_dog_voice1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$7", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（失望的低鸣）", "name": "义经"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$7"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "政宗？！义经？！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看来这不是一场梦。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_283_midn_1#1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰小姐！空爆！你们跑哪里去了！", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "char_283_midn_1#1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "2", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_284_spot_1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂——！你们两个，刚才失联了一分多钟，我还以为你们被沙子埋了呢！", "name": "斑点"}, "figure_art": "char_284_spot_1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰和空爆回头看去，只见自己熟悉的月见夜、斑点和泡普卡正朝她们跑来。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_283_midn_1#4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刚才突然起了一阵怪风，然后你们就失联了，我们都快急死了！还好战斗已经结束了。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "char_283_midn_1#4"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_283_midn_1#4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "月见夜", "content": "你们没事吧？"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_283_midn_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "月见夜", "content": "咦，你们什么时候换的衣服？还挺别致的。"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_284_spot_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何止是衣服，你们身后的云兽和牙兽又是从哪来的？看起来伙食很好的样子。", "name": "斑点"}, "figure_art": "char_284_spot_1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰姐姐！空爆姐姐！你们没事，真是太好了！", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#12$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看着眼前这三个自己再熟悉不过的“问题儿童”，又看了看身后那两个新伙伴，梓兰感到哭笑不得。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一瞬间，她想起了独立自主的宝巫迦，想起了那个开朗的斑弥罗，想起了那个为了守护重要之人和国家而变得固执的月见夜。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她觉得自己变了，变得温柔了一些。"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "具体的事情我会慢慢跟你们说。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "总而言之，月见夜，斑点，泡普卡，你们没事就好。这次任务的混乱，是我的指挥失误，让你们担心了，辛苦你们了。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_283_midn_1#4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "char_283_midn_1#4"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_284_spot_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斑点"}, "figure_art": "char_284_spot_1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#10$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？怎么了？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_284_spot_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂喂，你是谁啊？你不是我们的队长吧？我们的队长只会叹着气骂我们是问题儿童。", "name": "斑点"}, "figure_art": "char_284_spot_1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_283_midn_1#4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "确实......这温柔的语气，这坦率的道歉......小姐，你是不是被沙尘暴里的什么东西附身了？", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "char_283_midn_1#4"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我认识几个懂秘术的姐妹，要不我们去看一看吧？", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "char_283_midn_1#4"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊哦。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#14$2"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "梓兰", "content": "你们两个家伙！我难得想当个好队长你们还不乐意了是吧？！任务报告！"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.53", "scale": 1.05, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert03_d", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 50.0, "randomness": 60.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "梓兰", "content": "现在！"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.53", "scale": 1.1, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert03_d", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "fadetime": 0.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 50.0, "randomness": 60.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "梓兰", "content": "立刻！"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.53", "scale": 1.15, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert03_d", "xScale": 1.15, "yScale": 1.15, "fadetime": 0.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 50.0, "randomness": 60.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "梓兰", "content": "马上！"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把刚才发生的所有事情给我一五一十地写清楚！还有，月见夜！你又去哪里认识了懂秘术的姐妹，嗯？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert03_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_283_midn_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "报告长官，此事说来话长！", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "char_283_midn_1#2"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_284_spot_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......这回是梓兰没错了。那我继续看漫画了，月见夜，等你搞清楚发生了什么后，记得跟我说一声。", "name": "斑点"}, "figure_art": "char_284_spot_1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最好三十字以内。", "name": "斑点"}, "figure_art": "char_284_spot_1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，有的时候我也觉得有些事真怪不了梓兰姐。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#4$2"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰姐姐！", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#12$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 1.5, "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，还是我们家的泡普卡最好了。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对了，政宗。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喵？", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$4"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这样吧，要不然，你们跟我们一起，先回我们的家吧？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你们的家喵？", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$2"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没错，是一个叫罗德岛的好地方。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#5$2"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g3_impermanence_palace", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西城的市场可以再扩大一些，斑弥罗，你的那些新发明，也该让国民们都见识一下了。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没问题，陛下！我最新改良的“全自动兔团子机”，保证能让大家随时随地都吃到美味的团子！", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在此之前，我认为还有一件事要做。我们应该在都城的中央广场上，为我们的英雄们建一座雕像。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊......为了梓兰小姐、空爆小姐、政宗大人和义经大人，还有过往的“异兽猎人”们。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但愿他们已经平安回到自己的家乡了。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对了，如果可以的话，吾希望为“雷之主”也立一座雕像。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这是为何？", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#2$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾不是为了纪念它，或者可怜它......只是，为了记住它。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "泡影国确实应当记住“雷之主”。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们能做的，就是将他们的故事，和这个国家的历史一起，永远流传下去。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "说起来，还真是有点想念他们啊。虽然空爆老是嘲笑我的发明，但没有她的武器，我的击龙枪也确实造不出来。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还有政宗，那家伙虽然嘴碎，但给的东西都是真材实料......", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊......不知怎么的，虽然现在很和平，但总觉得......有些空落落的。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "月见夜和宝巫迦的视线再次相遇，这一次，不再有隔阂与对立。"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在这时，一名武士神色古怪地走了进来。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2106_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "启禀陛下、将军......城外有两位猎人求见。", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2106_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "猎人？来自哪里？", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#4$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2106_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她们说......她们来自遥远的大地——", "name": "武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2106_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宝巫迦心中一动，一种难以言喻的预感涌上心头。她快步走出议事厅，来到了城门前。"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "3"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "3", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g1_impermanence_street", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5, "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#1$2", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5, "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城门外，站着两个风尘仆仆的身影。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其中一人，身着一套如同紫色火焰般的优雅猎人套装，手持长弓，正警惕地打量着四周的环境。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而另一人，则一身青蓝色护甲，充满野性气息，背上背着一对巨大的剑盾，正一脸无聊地用脚尖踢着地上的石子。"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她们的衣着、神态、武器......都和宝巫迦记忆深处的那两个人有一些出入。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，那两张脸，却是一模一样。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5, "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#1$2", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5, "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我听说这里有值得挑战的野兽，才跋山涉水过来的，你这家伙，该不会想和我抢吧？", "name": "急躁的猎人"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#1$2", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5, "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是听说泡影国周边的野兽身上有非常稀有的素材，如果传闻属实，那就各凭本事。", "name": "冷静的猎人"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5, "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，那敢情好！", "name": "急躁的猎人"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......梓兰小姐？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......空爆小姐？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_coldforest", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "时空的撕扯感只是一瞬。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当雷狼龙再次睁开双眼时，扑面而来的，不再是泡影国地下遗迹那混合着尘土与“诅咒”的死寂气息。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是风。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是夹杂着潮湿泥土、青草芬芳和清冽水汽的风。是它自诞生之日起，就无比熟悉的风。"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它抬起头，皎洁的月光穿过茂密的树冠，在布满青苔的地面上洒下斑驳的银辉。它听到了远处瀑布的轰鸣，听到了林间虫豸的鸣叫。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它回来了。"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "压抑在身体里十年的、属于巫女的那份沉重力量已经消失，纠缠在灵魂中那份污浊的“诅咒”也已烟消云散。"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_normalroar1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它发出一声悠长的、不再带有痛苦与愤怒的咆哮。那吼声不再是为了威慑，而是为了宣告——这片山林真正的王者，回来了。"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_speedline", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_ridedragon_walk1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_ridedragon_walk2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_coldforest", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "fadetime": 1.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它开始奔跑。"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "矫健的四肢在林间飞跃，利爪刨开熟悉的泥土，强壮的身躯撞开挡路的灌木。"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_ridedragon_walk1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_ridedragon_walk2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_coldforest", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "fadetime": 1.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它跃过湍急的溪流，在瀑布下驻足，任由冰凉的水花冲刷着自己满是伤痕的鳞甲，洗去那不属于这个世界的尘埃。"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_ridedragon_walk1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_ridedragon_walk2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_coldforest", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "fadetime": 1.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它循着记忆，找到了一处悬崖。那里是它的王座。它安静地卧下，将巨大的头颅枕在前爪上，金色的长尾如疲倦的蛇般，盘在身侧。"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它闭上了眼睛，安然地陷入了沉睡。"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 1.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 1.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_coldforest", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啪。"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 1.0, "fillto": 0.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 1.0, "fillto": 0.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一声轻微的树枝断裂声，让它的耳朵猛地一抖。"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它瞬间睁开了双眼，兽瞳在黑夜中亮起，睡意荡然无存。"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它听到了。"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一种沉稳的、富有节奏的、属于两足生物的脚步声。一步，又一步，正不紧不慢地向这里靠近。"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那脚步声中，没有恐惧，只有坚定。"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷狼龙缓缓地站起身，望向声音传来的方向，一个身影从树林的阴影中走出。"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一个猎人，头戴着宽大的竹制斗笠，身上穿着红蓝相间的结云衣，脚下的木屐踩在岩石上，发出轻微而清脆的“嗒嗒”声。"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的手中，握着一把修长的太刀，刀身在月光下反射出内敛而锋利的光芒。"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他同样看到了悬崖上的雷狼龙。"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四目相对。"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没有憎恨，没有恐惧。"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_skillroar_normal", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$MHR_sys_monsterhunter2_intro", "key": "$MHR_sys_monsterhunter2_loop", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2102_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5, "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷狼龙的肌肉开始隆起，一缕缕金色的雷光开始在它蓝玉般的鳞甲上跳动、闪烁。它低下头，发出一声低沉的、充满了战意的咆哮。"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这是一种古老的、刻在它血脉中的宿命。"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它不理解何为“英雄”，也不在乎何为“牺牲”。"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它只知道，在它的世界里，当一位强者，与另一位强者相遇时，战斗，便是唯一的，也是最高的敬意。"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}